source: tests/snapshot/help_text.rs
expression: stdout
---
Check environment, configuration, and connectivity

  Exit code 0 if all checks pass or warn, 1 if any check fails. The
  --all flag overrides --profile and runs against every profile.

Usage:
  doctor [OPTIONS]

Options:
      --offline
          Skip network checks

      --all
          Check all profiles

  -h, --help
          Print help (see a summary with '-h')
